<HL>
   Economy:
   U.S. Manufacturers' Export Prospects
   Get Darker as Prices Fall, Dollar Rises
   ----
   By Clare Ansberry
   Staff Reporter of The Wall Street Journal
</HL>
<DATE>
06/20/91
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE A2
</SO>
<MS>
BASIC MATERIALS (BSC)
